{"type": "article", "id": 24239, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-03-22T07:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 1954, "name": "包装"}, {"id": 25215, "name": "RE.BIN"}, {"id": 25216, "name": "Edelkrone"}, {"id": 25217, "name": "Victor Branding"}, {"id": 25218, "name": "Jenifer Janniere"}, {"id": 25219, "name": "Simon Frambach"}, {"id": 25220, "name": "Garðar Eyjólfsson"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606161156C8p7M2Hagt1GqZsy.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>boutique hotels new collection by Jenifer Janniere</h2>\n<p>这一套家具是洛杉矶的女设计师 Jenifer Janniere 为精品酒店设计的，一共五件，包括床、边桌、落地柜、壁挂式烛台和架子。她使用了一种旧的青铜，除了做结构外还充当了图案本身，它们斜向相交组成具有几何感的线条图案，是左右对称的，体现了一种传统与现代的结合，很有个性。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071045120RWJVt4zXT7jI8Ev.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104512D8xEXb6RnOtivBWL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66805556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104513PphvkQiWymNtA97V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66805556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104513d32ezTSGs6iCb7ln.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66805556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104514CNReqg10rIahBEsK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Nod lamp by Simon Frambach</h2>\n<p>这是一盏极为简化的桌灯，它由一根长条形的柱子连接了圆片形的灯罩和底座。德国设计师 Simon Frambach 想要减少灯罩本身带来的阴影，于是设计成这种简化的结构。而圆片形灯罩本身就是一个可上下活动的开关，打开后灯光就慢慢出现，就像是翻开了笔记本电脑。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104514kViJrTIWjN4F5mAo.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.93162393\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104514UQmnK03PRgDESjvf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69123932\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104515D5pQEuAKtjPUBLiR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53952991\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104515zcgKxWqBayFSn87b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Sulphur Archive collection by Garðar Eyjólfsson </h2>\n<p>这一系列的托盘来自冰岛设计师 Garðar Eyjólfsson，他使用了硫磺这种很少用在家具领域的材料。他通过数控将玄武岩磨出一些空缺，然后将熔融后的硫磺倒入其中，形成了黑色和黄色的镶嵌纹路，有点像肥皂盒。另外将 100 度到 120 度的硫磺倒入纸模具，等待结晶，就形成了一些小的硫磺块，与黑色的玄武岩一起是很古典的搭配。<a href=\"http://eyjolfsson.com/Sulphur-Archive\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104516ldZh5Xq6UML7ky2z.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104516sidOVt2Jvu7DjTxa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65811966\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104517iArqu9NDxHYblfsP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104517pvasm54IKAfEcBVt.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.17200855\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104517XV9PFMpy31NOcRg6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>MODERN RECYCLING BIN by RE.BIN </h2>\n<p>这个垃圾筒使用了可回收塑料，像是直接由普通牛皮纸袋子做成的，只有黑白两色，方正而简单。但它的优点也在于这种清爽简洁，给环境的影响很弱，可以融入现代的家庭厨房到办公环境中。设计者的初衷也有环保的想法，让超市或商店都使用纸口袋，提回来之后，可以放在里面用做垃圾袋了。产品目前在众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/20614143/rebin-the-modern-alternative-to-traditional-recycl?ref=nav_search\">这里是众筹链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104518UPFYSf3eqAWGnOra.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104518kBqg1fCPycFLaodM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060710451960EVJFYTp5vfU1bZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104519OVWwCsLHYPQD63Ro.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104520tFYTdRC5h4MBkXP7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Oqloq by Edelkrone</h2>\n<p>这款时钟模糊了时间的概念，它只有一根指针和几乎看不见的刻度。更重要的是它将 24 小时完全摊在一个表面上，最高和最低点分别代表中午 12 点和晚上 12 点。最外圈有一层可自由排布的彩色的条纹，包括红、绿、白这几种颜色，相当于将一天的时间划分了几个部分而不是精确地看到真正分钟的刻度，对于每天只需要明确上下班这类关键时刻的人来说未尝不是简洁的表达方式。挂钟可轻易取下来调整，整体简洁干净。售价 99 美元，<a href=\"https://www.edelkrone.com/p/499/oqloq\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104520U3DzxhXjEqi2Hs4Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104521hE4x5iBF1t8slrRa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.37314815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104521qSuJ3Motlzrkm4I1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.28240741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104521uTrbe8kotYsMhjGN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071045228QuT1baDrHWl3c7O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Cha Tzu Tang by Victor Branding Design</h2>\n<p>茶籽堂（Cha Tzu Tang）是台湾一家以茶籽为基础发展洗护香油等产品的品牌。这是它们为第 51 届金马奖设计的礼品包装。包装上是版画家沐冉(Muran)采用木刻油印的方式画出的胭脂马，以点明金马奖，也拥有漂亮的手工感。盒子里用 5 个不一样的瓶子装有洗护用品，很精致。至少能让人感受到作为官方礼品的细心之处。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071045234Njamx7w90KFIRUY.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104523Hy7hAZet0W8SdVcm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104524AxJiRYM1jsV6rXPO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64351852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104524MFRBSGd7HQDc6bmV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}